# Input

```md
[hello][world]

[hello][]

[hello]

[  spaced  ][  label  ]

[*foo* bar][]

[foo][BaR]

text with [inline][ref] in the middle

[link with **bold**][ref]

[world]: https://example.com "World"
[  label  ]: https://example.com "Label"
[*foo* bar]: https://example.com "Foo Bar"
[BaR]: https://example.com "Bar"
[ref]: https://example.com "Ref"
[hello]: https://example.com "Hello"

```


# Formatted

```md
[hello][world]

[hello][]

[hello]

[  spaced  ][  label  ]

[*foo* bar][]

[foo][BaR]

text with [inline][ref] in the middle

[link with **bold**][ref]

[world]: https://example.com "World"
[ label ]: https://example.com "Label"
[*foo* bar]: https://example.com "Foo Bar"
[BaR]: https://example.com "Bar"
[ref]: https://example.com "Ref"
[hello]: https://example.com "Hello"

```
